{"tid":2500864,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"曾志偉抗疫電影《總是有愛在隔離》開畫票房慘敗，不敵ViuTV演員電影","createTime":"2021-04-23T03:26:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T04:03:22.000Z","uid":134071,"like":76,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"50bfd45378ab564fe3830eeb812e59a6bc46da5b","tid":2500864,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:26:12.000Z","msg":"曾志偉早前曾暗串ViuTV只係小眾台，但佢自己主演既新片，雖然有TVB力捧，香港開畫票房卻不敵由ViuTV演員主演既電影！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《總是有愛在隔離》係由曾志偉一手拉線既抗疫電影，主演演員包括<strong>曾志偉</strong>和<strong>梁家輝</strong>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且，根據探子回報，TVB上星期既垃圾綜藝節目，曾經撥出一大段去全力宣傳《總是有愛在隔離》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n結果，《總是有愛在隔離》於4月22日係香港開畫，<strong>單日開畫票房不足9萬</strong>，低過由ViuTV視帝劉俊謙主演既《幻愛》。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然，《幻愛》單日開畫票房15萬，其實都係非常慘淡既數字，導演周冠威直言曾為此感到情緒低落。點知《總是有愛在隔離》輸得更慘，唔知曾志偉而家既情緒會係點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《幻愛》後來票房反彈至1525萬（主要因為電影本身高質，但亦要多謝唔少手足幫手吹雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）， 但《總是有愛在隔離》票房應該無機會反彈。馬雲旗下既南華早報，都對《總是有愛在隔離》作出劣評 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n藍絲曾志偉，而家邊個係小數派？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/81817\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfilmblog.com%2Farchives%2F81817&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrfhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=b1860823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/81817</a><br />\n<br />\n《總是有愛在隔離》看來首天已被觀眾隔離，首天於49院映180場，僅錄得近千六人次，每場平均人次只有九位，推算收入不足九萬，當中已包括一場包場。《總》片以為香港電影工作者籌款為名，可是整部電影卻予人過氣感覺，而且電影的喜劇包裝與現實情況距離甚遠，令觀眾對電影興趣甚低，群星拱照也沒有星光可言。<br />\n<br />\n仍在上映電影方面，五部電影仍在十大之中，當中英皇發行、陳茂賢執導的《不日成婚》在第四周於33院映逾75場下，昨獲逾千人次捧場，每場平均人次達13，推算收入接近七萬，為電影於今天累積達470萬，看來五百萬指日可徒。而環球發行、趙善恆執導的《一秒拳王》在上映第七周仍十大之中，昨映近75場獲逾850人次，推算收入接近六萬。觀乎目前距離千六萬大關只差廿多萬，相信周日可以達標。"},{"pid":"89ad1c1745627f7f2c4f19633a73315b51b32be6","tid":2500864,"uid":134071,"like":73,"dislike":2,"score":71,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:26:34.000Z","msg":"同時，《一秒拳王》繼續好評上映中，票房準備破1600萬。<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n戲院場次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hkmovie6.com/movie/edd50852-0223-450e-824d-f68c17d146b6/showtime\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkmovie6.com%2Fmovie%2Fedd50852-0223-450e-824d-f68c17d146b6%2Fshowtime&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrfhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=a6a7f58f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkmovie6.com/movie/edd50852-0223-450e-824d-f68c17d146b6/showtime</a><br />\n<br />\n預告片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w-TUj_wSSZs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dw-TUj_wSSZs&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrfhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=c8aa2e98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w-TUj_wSSZs</a>"},{"pid":"74325c87bfc9cfd8b1bd07fc1d3f1f899894cae5","tid":2500864,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:28:09.000Z","msg":"Super<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7499d0dcf38858c83e7f231e374420179ea501","tid":2500864,"uid":53062,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:28:10.000Z","msg":"呢套野搵堆明星炒埋一碟，想好睇都難"},{"pid":"a9c3201e89dd7928ce1ad79664f8a8a743206789","tid":2500864,"uid":290118,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:28:30.000Z","msg":"唔講都唔知，咩戲嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1824c4b8e94d9e2b86bb996bbf62b8c94572672e","tid":2500864,"uid":30040,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:28:35.000Z","msg":"疫情未完仲上映D疫情既電影？去睇既係咩心態？<img src=\"/a